proxmox-frr-templates (0.1.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * change route maps template to adapt to new frr types. Instead of defining
    every potential match / set type manually under a different name,
    proxmox-frr now uses the adjacently-tagged representation for serializing
    key/value pairs for match/set actions. This allows simplifying the
    route_maps template by simply rendering the respective key / value fields.

